description: You stand in a deep dark freezer. You try to move, but yet...you
can't. You feel nothing, all there is your mind. You see
other mortals in here, standing in place. You have been frozen
and placed in the Mortal Freezer. Have Fun.

description: You stand amounst fire and brimestone.  Torutured souls slave away,
dragging large bolders, and being whipped by a demon.  Flames burn
everywhere, and molten earth flows around, like a large river.
Welcome to hell, mother fucker.

description: A thunderous roar fills the stadium as you clamber to find your seat and
witness the upcoming arena match.  You see bloodstains on the very front
benches from particularly gruesome matches of the past, and you try to find
a clean patch of bench and get comfortable.  For whom will you cheer to
reign victorious over the corpse of his fallen opponent?

description: You stand on a large desk.  Above you the massive airship looms as you

statue of each god stands, Cyric, Nisstyre, Talos, Teron, Selune,

justice only.
